/*
 * ls_setdebug
 *
 * Parameters:
 *
 * ServPort: server port for RPC.
 * debug_ptr: pointer to the new debug record.
 * debug_size: size of the debug record in 32-bit words.
 *
 * Results: none
 *
 * Side effects:
 *
 * Updates the global debug record.
